Charge Pending Stripe Invoices on Demand
text:
Hi everyone , if most of your stripe payments don't come through because of insufficient funds (or any other reason), I made a bot that you can use to charge your clients with unpaid invoices on specific dates. I use it mainly to charge on the 15th and the 30th of each month, since these are the dates that people usually have money.
If you're interesred in this tool. You can text me at +529992070830 or just contact me on IG @hec_olguin
Best of luck for your startup!
